cast.overview: While under the guise of taking his family on a weekend winter getaway, Loid's attempt to make progress on his current mission Operation Strix proves difficult when Anya mistakenly gets involved and triggers events that threaten world peace.
cast.title: SPY x FAMILY CODE: White

details.biography:
Natsumi Fujiwara (藤原 夏海, Fujiwara Natsumi, born June 2, 1994) is a Japanese voice actress from Hamamatsu City, Shizuoka Prefecture. She is managed by the agency Arts Vision. She graduated from Nihon Narration Engi Kenkyujo (Japan Narration Acting Institute) in the same class as Kaede Hondo.

In her second year since her debut, she played her first leading role as Chihiro Komiya in the 2016 tv anime Shonen Maid. In 2021, she won the Best New Actress Award at the 15th Seiyu Awards. Her hobbies and special skills are singing, playing catch, high bar (artistic gymnastics), and kendama.
details.name: Natsumi Fujiwara
